Technology and cloud blog which discusses emergent topics with great impact around the world in short, medium and long term.

Eduardo es un estudiante  de ultimo ano de computer science

Eduardo is a mexican student, taking its last year in Computer Science. He has worked in different technical companies, but also in others within different areas just to achieve diversity in terms of experiences. He has travelled the world trying to learn about other cultures, customs, and their technological development. He writes about Software Engineering, Cloud Computing, and general topics surrounding our daily life because of the technology unstopable growth. 

-----

Después de ser seleccionado para el Internship en Infosys, India, logré platicar con un profesor que comentaba que las plazas de trabajo para gente en el área de Computer Science y Software Engineering, estaba haciéndose menos debido al crecimiento y demanda en países que brindan servicios como terceros, tales como India, Brasil o México.

